thunder trail is a 1941 american western film directed by lesley selander and written by dorrell mcgowan and stuart e. mcgowan . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , john miljan , ernest truex , william elmer , horace mcmahon , william frawley , andy clyde , rand brooks , ernest torrence , and jack hoxie . the film was released on june 8 , 1941 , by republic pictures .